c_{f} & = & \frac{2\Delta tu_{n}}{|\mathbf{x}_{C}-\mathbf{x}_{N}|}
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

 are the cells either side of 
